# ── 3. DIRECT JUMP TO T=0.4 (no quench, no aging) ────────────────────────────
# This is the critical difference from kovacs_memory.in.
# We go straight from liquid → T=0.4, bypassing the T=0.3 history.
# This glass will equilibrate to the same TEMPERATURE as the Kovacs glass
# but will have a completely different structural history.
fix             2 all nvt temp 2.0 0.4 0.1
run             30000                           # ramp down from T=2.0 to T=0.4
